{"tid":987501,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（認真求教）有個肥婆friend成日妒忌你你會點面對？","createTime":"2019-01-19T11:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T13:57:04.000Z","uid":163962,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"94ca6b89fdb3d9c107ad1aec37208f41bb2a07c2","tid":987501,"uid":163962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T11:09:00.000Z","msg":"我係絲 有個中同中一識到依加二十頭 我以前都係瘦底但就皮膚差 個樣都一般 但由十八九歲開始皮膚好返曬  而且有返個雙眼皮 有做下運動 越大越靚 係老師同男女同學都都讚嗰種 外表十分你當我有七至八分。但個肥婆friend 就由細到大都肥同矮 成日換畫因為佢啲男朋友全部係skout 識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲笑我冇拖拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我其實知佢一向妒忌我比中學嗰陣靚左好多 完全兩個人咁 但天生有咩值得討厭 我都有唔靚嘅時候 中學皮膚差冇左成個中學生涯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  依加我靚左作為朋友唔係應該鄧人開心咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但佢就暗中討厭我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打絲打覺得係咪當冇左個friend算 真心好討厭依種虛偽朋友關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e44ffce286fbf6f7aa3065bd871f9399c4dc1ac","tid":987501,"uid":163962,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T11:10:20.000Z","msg":"定係一直扮friend 算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e073f868da5820e817c458cd134b67fa57bd324","tid":987501,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T11:11:02.000Z","msg":"女仔，個個都係咁陰險"},{"pid":"b68fdcdca185f9414660ef11cea08b828e4493e4","tid":987501,"uid":69484,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T11:11:48.000Z","msg":"題材有討論空間 <br />\n但係假膠 <br />\n負皮 上一頁"},{"pid":"64c10c73b42acde448c9d90d4da09fc7001318e6","tid":987501,"uid":163962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T11:13:24.000Z","msg":"真架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  用啊哥ac"},{"pid":"845537da148f9f748d4266be6ad3a3041acd0b7e","tid":987501,"uid":163962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc